      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i'm telling u it feels intentional. like the beat drops slightly off or there's this weird high-pitched ringing that only happens when i'm listening to certain artists. if spotify is just \"standard music files\" how do they explain how they could slip those sub-audible patterns in without anyone noticing? i feel like i'm being steered towards certain moods or thoughts.",
